  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK1061">
<l>karavā tuvantīyuṅ kaṇṇaṉṉār kaṇṇu </l>
<l>miravāmai kōṭi yuṟum</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Not to beg (at all) even from those excellent persons who cheerfully give without refusing, will do immense good.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
